name: FEEL FREE AND CONFIDENT
description:
Comparing yourself with others both on social media and in the real world is also one of the symptoms that can cause a lack of self-confidence that you have.
Sometimes someone who has physical advantages gets special privileges from others, both in the form of treatment and words, gifts from God.
Another gift given by God is the different abilities of each individual, which we must practice in order to reach the best of our potential.
So, stop comparing yourself to others, you have your own strengths and weaknesses,
Come to terms with it, show your best version with confidence
